dct_description_sm: Includes index, tourist notes, color illustrations, 3 inset maps, and 5 ancillary maps. Includes insets: International air routes -- Administrative-territorial division -- Distance between cities (km). Relief shown by gradient tints, shading and heights.
dct_publisher_sm: Dushanbe : SUE "Map Factory" of the Land Management, Geodesy and Cartography Agency under the Government of the Republic of Tajikistan, 2009.
